=== Pronunciations ===
kyar-uh-score-uhst

key-are-uh-score-uhst

kyar-oh-scur-ist


=== Definition ===
an artist in chiaroscuro (pictorial representation in terms of light and shade without regard for or use of colors in the objects depicted.


=== Etymology ===
Italian chiaroscuro, English suffix -ist


=== Information ===
Chiaroscurist was the winning word of Jody-Anne Maxwell in the 1998 Scripps National Spelling Bee.